<h2 id="4-publish-your-package">4. Publish your package</h2>

<style>
.youtube {
    width: 100%; height: 46.87vw;
    border: none; background: transparent;
} @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .youtube {
        width: 42vw; height: 23.625vw;
    }
